1. On *krade* novac iz kase. (He steals money from the cash register.)
2. Nije prvi put da se *krade* u ovom kraju. (It's not the first time that stealing happens in this area.)
3. *Krade* se sve više bicikala po gradu. (Bike theft is increasing in the city.)
4. Žena koja je *ukrala* torbicu je uhapšena. (The woman who stole the purse was arrested.)
5. Ne možemo dopustiti da nam *ukradu* izbore. (We can't allow someone to steal the elections from us.)
6. Ne znam ko mi je *ukrao* mobilni telefon. (I don't know who stole my cellphone.)
7. Koliko novca si *ukrala* iz moje torbe? (How much money did you steal from my purse?)
8. Policija traga za lopovima koji su *ukrali* dragocenosti. (The police are searching for thieves who stole valuables.)
9. Nemoj da *kradeš* kolače iz frižidera. (Don't steal cakes from the fridge.)
10. Dete je *ukralo* slatkiše iz prodavnice. (The child stole sweets from the store.)